Instruct the OIC-Municipal Treasurer to ensure that paid DVs are intact as listed in the RCI upon transmittal to the Office of the Accountant; and
Instruct the Municipal Accountant and OIC-Municipal Treasurer to always transmit complete submission of accounts to facilitate thorough audit and verification of the agency’s financial transactions.

